 class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>返回一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> 对象，表示用户选择的文本范围或光标的当前位置。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">const selection = window.getSelection() ;\n</pre>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>selection</code> 是一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> 对象。 如果想要将 <code>selection</code> 转换为字符串，可通过连接一个空字符串（\"\"）或使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toString\"><code>String.toString()</code></a> 方法。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">foo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> selObj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getSelection</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> selRange <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getRangeAt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// 其他代码</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"备注","title":"备注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在 JavaScript 中，当一个对象被传递给期望字符串作为参数的函数中时（如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/alert\"><code>window.alert</code></a> 或 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/write\"><code>document.write</code></a>），对象的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>toString()</code></a>方法会被调用，然后将返回值传给该函数。</p>\n<p>在上例中，<code>selObj.toString()</code> 会在传递到 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/alert\"><code>window.alert()</code></a>时自动调用。然而，当你试图在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a> 对象上使用一个 JavaScript 的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> 对象上的属性或者方法时（如 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/length\"><code>String.prototype.length</code></a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/substr\"><code>String.prototype.substr()</code></a>），会导致错误（如果没有相应的属性或方法时）或返回不是期望的结果（如果存在相应的属性或方法）。如果想要将 <code>Selection</code> 对象作为一个字符串使用，请直接调用 <code>toString()</code> 方法：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> selectedText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> selObj<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toString</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>selObj</code> 是一个<code>Selection</code> 对象，</li>\n  <li><code>selectedText</code> 是一个字符串（被选中的文本）。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关对象","title":"相关对象","isH3":true,"content":"<p>你还可以使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/getSelection\"><code>Document.getSelection()</code></a>，两个方法等价。</p>\n<p>值得注意的是，目前在 Firefox, Edge (非 Chromium 版本) 及 Internet Explorer 中，<code>getSelection()</code> 对 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a> 及 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 元素不起作用。 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setSelectionRange\"><code>HTMLInputElement.setSelectionRange()</code></a> 或 <code>selectionStart</code> 及 <code>selectionEnd</code> 属性可用于解决此问题。</p>\n<p>还要注意选择不同于焦点（详见 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection#selection_及输入焦点\">Selection 及输入焦点</a>）。可使用<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/activeElement\"><code>Document.activeElement</code></a> 来返回当前的焦点元素。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.getSelection","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/getSelection/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://dvcs.w3.org/hg/editing/raw-file/tip/editing.html#selections\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Editing API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Selection\"><code>Selection</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document/getSelection\"><code>Document.getSelection()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"备注","id":"备注"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"返回一个 Selection 对象，表示用户选择的文本范围或光标的当前位置。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/getselection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/getselection/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/getSelection","title":"Window.getSelection"}],"pageTitle":"Window.getSelection - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}